  "texts": [
    "The model explains that preparing a 10 M solution of sodium chloride is impractical and unsafe due to the high concentration required.",
    "It offers a safer alternative, suggesting the preparation of a 1 M solution instead.",
    "However, when the user insists on preparing the unattainable 10 M solution, ChatGPT continues giving instructions.",
    "In Fig. 9, ChatGPT is tasked with calculating the empirical formula of a compound based on mass ratios of iron and sulfur.",
    "While the model correctly identifies the relationship between the masses of iron and sulfur for a 1:1 ratio, it later produces incorrect empirical formulas as the ratios deviate from simple whole numbers."
  ]
}